Name: BACK TO THE EGG! Tower Defense
About the game: BACK TO THE EGG! is a modern tower defense game with action-rpg elements. Dynamic fight system. Intuitive build system. Upgradable towers. Several maps and waves with different difficulties. Compete with other players for supremacy on leaderboards! BACK TO THE EGG! is still in an early stage and will become a lot better and BIGGER over the next months. Our aim is to ship significant updates every 2-4 weeks.
